==Farsi==
===Noun===
'''فارسی''' (Fārsī)

# [[Persian]], the major language of ancient [[Persia]] and modern [[Iran]], [[Afghanistan]] and [[Tajikistan]] and is widely spoken in [[Uzbekistan]]. However the version spoken in countries other than Iran is called Ordo and Pashto. The Persian Language was originated in Iran ,and the countries listed above were part of Iran at the time.

